243:8080/was40/lqz/lqzhjinian.htm" target="_blank" class="nslog:1968">【李清照·纪念遗存】<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a><span>．济南图书馆</span><span>&#91;引用日期2013-09-7&#93;</span>．</p>   </li> <li class="layout" id="reference-[11]-5444734-wrap">  <p class="refUrl"><span class="ref-index">11．</span><a class="ref-top"  name="refIndex_11_5444734" id="refIndex_11_5444734" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[11]_5444734">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><a rel="nofollow" href="http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2006-03-21/03118486594s.shtml" target="_blank" class="nslog:1968">李清照纪念馆有多少<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a><span>．新浪网</span><span>&#91;引用日期2013-09-7&#93;</span>．</p>   </li> <li class="layout" id="reference-[12]-5444734-wrap">  <p class="refUrl"><span class="ref-index">12．</span><a class="ref-top"  name="refIndex_12_5444734" id="refIndex_12_5444734" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[12]_5444734">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><a rel="nofollow" href="http://lady.fengone.com/lady/20130521/440776.html" target="_blank" class="nslog:1968">千古第一才女——李清照<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a><span>．凤网</span><span>&#91;引用日期2013-09-7&#93;</span>．</p>   </li> <li class="layout" id="reference-[13]-5444734-wrap">  <p class="refUrl"><span class="ref-index">13．</span><a class="ref-top"  name="refIndex_13_5444734" id="refIndex_13_5444734" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[13]_5444734">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a><a rel="nofollow" href="http://218.56.50.243:8080/was40/lqz/lqzhyanjiu.htm" target="_blank" class="nslog:1968">历代名家评论 <span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a><span>．济南图书馆</span><span>&#91;引用日期2013-09-7&#93;</span>．</p>   </li>  </ul> </dd></dl><dl id="viewExtCati"  class="nslog-area log-set-param" log-set-param="module_tag" data-nslog-type="19"> <dt class="open-tag-title">词条标签：</dt> <dd> <a href="/fenlei/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B8%85%E7%85%A7%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81" target="_blank" class="open-tag  nslog:7336">李清照作品</a><a href="/fenlei/%E5%AE%8B%E8%AF%8D%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6" target="_blank" class="open-tag open-tag-mr7 nslog:7336">宋词四大家</a>    <a class="taglist" href="/taglist?tag=%C5%AE%D0%D4&amp;tagfromview" target="_blank">女性</a>    ，  <a class="taglist" href="/taglist?tag=%C0%FA%CA%B7%C8%CB%CE%EF&amp;tagfromview" target="_blank">历史人物</a>    ，  <a class="taglist" href="/taglist?tag=%C8%CB%CE%EF&amp;tagfromview" target="_blank">人物</a>    ，  <a class="taglist" href="/taglist?tag=%B4%CA%C8%CB&amp;tagfromview" target="_blank">词人</a>    ，  <a class="taglist" href="/taglist?tag=%CB%CE%B3%AF&amp;tagfromview" target="_blank">宋朝</a>  </dd></dl><div class="clear"></div><div class="clear"></div></div></div> <script type="text/javascript">(function(){window.rsInsertData = window['rsInsertData']||[];rsdataList = {"top":[],"foot":[]};if(rsdataList.top||rsdataList.foot){if(false) {delete rsdataList.top;window.specialCardType = true;}rsInsertData.push([5444736, rsdataList]);}window.refTipData = window['refTipData']||[];rfdataList = [{"index":1,"type":1,"title":"\u8d8a\u5267\u8d44\u6599\u6765\u6e90","url":"http:\/\/zhaoyuan0622.blog.163.com\/blog\/static\/16050510201101375354154\/","site":"","publishDate":"","refDate":""},{"index":2,"type":1,"title":"\u201c\u9996\u5c4a\u6c5f\u82cf\u827a\u672f\u5c55\u6f14\u6708\u201d\u597d\u770b\u4e0d\u8d35","url":"http:\/\/roll.sohu.com\/20130528\/n377229991.shtml","site":"\u641c\u72d0\u7f51","publishDate":"2013-05-28","refDate":"2013-05-28"}];refTipData.push([5444736, rfdataList]);})();if(false) {window.specialCardJibing = true;}</script><div class="clear"></div><a name="sub5444736" subversionid="43350068" id="sub5444736" class="sub-anchor">&nbsp;</a><div id="sec-header1" class="rbheader-0 b-ent-section b-rlt b-clearfix sprite-bg low-lh nslog:517 " log-data-detail="{subindex:2}"> <h2 class="b-h2-3 bk-sidecatalog-title"><span class="headline-index">2.</span><span class="headline-content">越剧作品</span></h2> <span class="b-ent-section-action"><a style="display:none;" id="tpl-5444736" href="/tpldivideload?lemmaId=3066&subLemmaId=5444736" target="blank" class="b-btn-1 b-ent-section-action-edit small sprite-bg med-slv-bdr"><span class="med-slv-bdr"><em class="tpldidicon"></em></span></a>  <a href="#" data-edit-id="3066:5444736" class="nslog:511 b-btn-1 b-ent-section-action-edit small sprite-bg med-slv-bdr"><span class="med-slv-bdr"><em class="sprite"></em>编辑本义项</span></a>  <a href="#" class="b-btn-1 b-ent-section-action-toggle small sprite-bg med-slv-bdr nslog:518"><span class="med-slv-bdr"><em class="sprite"></em></span></a> </span> <span class="dir-holder sprite" style="top:33px;bottom:0;"></span></div><div id="sec-content1" subLemmaId="5444736" class="rainbowlemma-0 polysemy-item-cnt clearfix lazyload" lazy-path="/static/lemma/ui/view/describeTips/describeTips.js" lazy-init="e.init('sec-content1')" style="text-align:left;display:none;"><script>if (!baikeInfo.expFlag){if (!baikeInfo.hash[0] || !baikeInfo.lemmaHashFound){document.getElementById("sec-content0").style.display = "";baikeViewInfo.expIndex = 0;baikeInfo.expFlag = true;} else if (baikeInfo.hash[0] == 5444736) {document.getElementById("sec-content1").style.display = "";baikeViewInfo.expIndex = "1";baikeViewInfo.subLemmaId="5444736";baikeViewInfo.subVersionId="43350068";baikeInfo.expFlag = true;if(baikeInfo.hash[2]){window.location.hash = baikeInfo.hash[2];}else if(baikeInfo.hash[1]){window.location.hash = baikeInfo.hash[1];}}}</script><div class="bk-editable-lemma-btns"><span class="throwbtl-link-span" data-edit-id="5444736越剧作品3066" type="lemmaMulit"></span><span style="height:100%"></span></div><h1 class="title sub-title" id="lemmaTitle-5444736">李清照 </h1><script>window.PDC && PDC.first_screen && PDC.first_screen();</script><div id="lemmaContent-1" class="lemma-main-content rainbowlemma-0-"><div class="para">新编<a target=_blank href=/view/1052232.htm>古装剧</a>。<a target=_blank href=/view/946996.htm>罗怀臻</a>1998年编剧。</div>
<div class="para"><b>剧情简介：</b></div>
<div class="para"><div class="text_pic layoutright" data-layout="right" style="width:220px;float:right;"><a hidefocus="true" class="nslog:1199" href="/picview/3066/5444736/0/9e7ce6dc09f06c98cc11660f.html" target="_blank" style="height: 165px;width:220px;display:block;position:relative;"><img onload="this.className = this.className.replace('lazy-img','');" class="editorImg lazy-img log-set-param" log-set-param="img_view" alt="越剧《李清照》" title="越剧《李清照》" height="165" width="220" data-src="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=e1f1f706b80e7bec27da04e31f2fb9fa/810a19d8bc3eb135eb0a54b2a61ea8d3fc1f44ee.jpg"/><div id="lemma-img-tip"></div></a><p class="pic-info"><a class="nslog:1200 pic-handle" title="查看图片" href="/picview/3066/5444736/0/9e7ce6dc09f06c98cc11660f.html" target="_blank">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>越剧《李清照》</p></div>写宋代少女李清照，在秋千上与年轻的学者赵明诚吟诗诵词，结为知音。婚后，夫妻志同道合，相敬如宾，沉浸在诗词创作和《金石录》的编撰之中。10年后，赵明诚赴任离家，夫妻聚少离多。金人入侵中原，李清照经历了国亡家破、背井离乡、丈夫病死异乡、古董尽数被骗的一迭迭苦痛与灾难。直到晚年，李清照仍不能回到魂牵梦萦的故乡。因为痛、因为愁、因为太多的无望与绝望，她曾有过沉落。然而，正是人生的大不幸与社会的大动荡，才更加提升了作为乱世女词人李清照的词格和人格，她为后人留下了一首首千古传诵不绝的精美词章。</div>
<div class="para">该剧以女词人之纯、少妇之爱、中年之悲、暮年之哀为主线，用李清照12首著名诗词作链接，反映了女词人在追求美好理想却历经悲壮的人生中，夫妻携手守护优秀传统文化、忧国忧民、借词抗争的高尚人格和爱国主义情怀。</div>
<div class="para"><b>获奖情况：</b></div>
<div class="para">南京市越剧团为创作排练好这个剧目，历时2年余，经10易其稿，于2001年在南宁市举行的第七届中国戏剧节中一展风采，获<a target=_blank href=/view/1237607.htm>中国曹禺戏剧奖</a>优秀剧目奖、优秀编剧奖、优秀导演奖（<a target=_blank href=/view/3343548.htm>曹其敬</a>、<a target=_blank href=/view/2156852.htm>韩林根</a>）、优秀音乐奖（音乐作曲吴小平、唱腔设计王水庚、诗词领唱樊建萍）、优秀舞美设计奖（舞美设计周本义、张海豹、俞辉，灯光设计伊天夫、杨庆锦，服装设计蓝玲、马砚波，化妆设计蓝玲、徐霞英、王伟）、优秀表演奖（<a target=_blank href=/view/804702.htm>陶琪</a>饰李清照，<a target=_blank href=/view/2521667.htm>华洁</a>饰赵明诚）等大奖及表演奖（盛月芳、沈秋萍）共21个单项奖。<sup>[1]</sup><a name="ref_[1]_5444736"></a></div>
<div class="para">2013年，在4月28日到5月26日期间的“首届江苏艺术展演月”中，南京市越剧团的越剧《李清照》荣获“优秀剧目展演奖”。<sup>[2]</sup><a name="ref_[2]_5444736"></a></div>
