><td class="cardFirstTd">导演：</td><td class="cardSecondTd">李兆华</td></tr></table></td><td class="seperateTd"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="95%" align="right"><tr><td class="cardFirstTd">编剧：</td><td class="cardSecondTd">许文浩</td></tr><tr><td class="cardFirstTd">主演：</td><td class="cardSecondTd"><a target=_blank href=/view/168018.htm>刘雪华</a>，<a target=_blank href=/view/7019564.htm>何英伟</a></td></tr><tr><td class="cardFirstTd">集数：</td><td class="cardSecondTd">两集</td></tr><tr><td class="cardFirstTd">类型：</td><td class="cardSecondTd">古装，历史，人物</td></tr><tr><td class="cardFirstTd">上映时间：</td><td class="cardSecondTd">1988年09月08日</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></div></div></div> <div class="text_dir nslog-area log-set-param" log-set-param="catalogshow" data-nslog-type="1016" id="catalog-2" data-subindex="2"><p>目录</p><dl id="catalog-holder-2" class='holder'><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#2-1" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">基本信息</a></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#2-2" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">演员表</a></dd><dd class="catalog-item"><a href="#2-3" class="nslog:1274 " catalog="true" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">原声音乐</a></dd></dl><dl id="catalog-holder-2-2" class="holder2"></dl></div><div class="clear"></div> <script>window.PDC && PDC.first_screen && PDC.first_screen();</script><div id="lemmaContent-2" class="lemma-main-content rainbowlemma-0-"><h2 class="headline-1"><span class="text_edit editable-title" data-edit-id="3066:7791765:1"><a href="#" class="nslog:1019">编辑本段</a></span><a name="2-1"></a><a name="sub7791765_1"></a><span class="headline-content">基本信息</span></h2><div class="para">本剧是1988年香港亚洲电视邀请刘雪华出演的一部讲述宋代女词人李清照从出嫁到孤独终老的一生的电视剧。在剧中，刘雪华运用高超的演技将李清照的一颦一笑表现得出神入化，并将李清照的一生诠释得入木三分，获得一致好评。本剧分上、下两集，于1988年9月8日在香港首播。</div><h2 class="headline-1"><span class="text_edit editable-title" data-edit-id="3066:7791765:2"><a href="#" class="nslog:1019">编辑本段</a></span><a name="2-2"></a><a name="sub7791765_2"></a><span class="headline-content">演员表</span></h2><div class="module-common-1-container module-common-1-self log-set-param lazyload" lazy-init="e.commonLink('actor','7791765');" lazy-path="/static/lemma/ui/view/page_commonModule/page_commonModule.js" id="7791765-actor-div" log-set-param="view_commonModule_show" style="margin-bottom:14px"><span id="7791765-actor-refcon" class="common-refcon-1"></span><table id="7791765-actor-table" class="module-common-table-1 module-common-table-actor log-set-param" log-set-param="actor_show"><thead><tr><th class="commmonModule-th module-common-title-font" width="110">角色</th><th class="commmonModule-th module-common-title-font" width="110">演员</th><th class="commmonModule-th module-common-title-font" width="200">备注</th></tr></thead><tbody id='7791765-actor-0' style='' class='common-hide-tbody'><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/3066.htm>李清照</a></td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/168018.htm>刘雪华</a></td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/16633.htm>赵明诚</a></td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/7019564.htm>何英伟</a></td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/1884352.htm>秋兰</a></td><td class="">张碧儿</td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/225635.htm>赵挺之</a></td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/1111188.htm>郑雷</a></td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/216504.htm>李格非</a></td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/2221640.htm>司马华龙</a></td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/81897.htm>陈东</a></td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/1571489.htm>郑恕峰</a></td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class="">张飞乡</td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/1253382.htm>关伟伦</a></td><td class="">----</td></tr><tr><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/view/50413.htm>胡铨</a></td><td class=""><a target=_blank href=/