<div class="para">作词：李清照</div>
<div class="para">作曲：<a target=_blank href=/view/7429834.htm>关圣佑</a></div>
<div class="para">演唱：李宝容</div>
<div class="para">薄雾浓云<div class="album-view layoutright log-set-param" data-layout="right" log-set-param="album_view" style="width:240px"><p class="album-div" style="height:200px;width:240px;"><span class="album-border2" style="height:180px;width:220px;"></span><span class="album-border3" style="height:180px;width:220px;"></span><a hidefocus="true" class="album-overlay nslog:1212" href="/albums/3066/7791765/1/2214502.html#2214502$" target="_blank" style="height:200px;width:240px;"><img onload="this.className = this.className.replace('lazy-img','');" class="album-cover lazy-img" alt="《李清照》剧照" title="《李清照》剧照" height="180" width="220" data-src="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=8223b88f6b63f624185d3e01b745eb32/caef76094b36acaf5ee1a54a7cd98d1001e99c06.jpg" /><span class="album-logo"></span></a></p><span class="title">《李清照》剧照</span><span class="count">(20张)</span></div>愁永昼，</div>
<div class="para">瑞脑消金兽。</div>
<div class="para">佳节又重阳，</div>
<div class="para">玉枕纱厨，</div>
<div class="para">半夜凉初透。</div>
<div class="para">东篱把酒黄昏后，</div>
<div class="para">有暗香盈袖。</div>
<div class="para">莫道不消魂，</div>
<div class="para">帘卷西风，</div>
<div class="para">人比黄花瘦。</div>
<div class="para">人比黄花瘦。</div>

