<div class="para">丛 书 名：中国历代文人长篇传记小说<div class="text_pic layoutright" data-layout="right" style="width:150px;float:right;"><a hidefocus="true" class="nslog:1199" href="/picview/3066/10282374/0/0ff41bd5ad6eddc441f747d838dbb6fd52663384.html" target="_blank" style="height: 220px;width:150px;display:block;position:relative;"><img onload="this.className = this.className.replace('lazy-img','');" class="editorImg lazy-img log-set-param" log-set-param="img_view" alt="李清照" title="李清照" height="220" width="150" data-src="http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=c12475cd9d82d158bf825eb3b00a19d5/0ff41bd5ad6eddc441f747d838dbb6fd52663384.jpg"/><div id="lemma-img-tip"></div></a><p class="pic-info"><a class="nslog:1200 pic-handle" title="查看图片" href="/picview/3066/10282374/0/0ff41bd5ad6eddc441f747d838dbb6fd52663384.html" target="_blank">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>李清照</p></div></div>
<div class="para">出 版 社：上海文艺出版社</div>
<div class="para">ISBN：9787532136063</div>
<div class="para">出版时间：2009-08-01</div>
